2019年8月19日，{{Vgname-nb|坎巴拉太空计划2|en=Kerbal Space Program 2}}预计于2020年年中发布的消息在[[Gamescom|Gamescom]] 2019上发布。该游戏由{{tsl|en|Private Division}}开发。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kerbal Space Program 2 is delayed|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/kerbal-space-program-2-is-delayed/|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2019-11-07|last=Chalk|first=Andy|work=PC Gamer|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223064957/https://www.pcgamer.com/kerbal-space-program-2-is-delayed/|archive-date=2020-02-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>续作将会延续《坎巴拉太空计划》的沙盒特性，同时加入新的推进方式（如[[獵戶座計劃|猎户座计划]]）、用于建造轨道或行星基地的居住模块、多人模式和星际旅行功能（以前此功能只能通过MOD实现）。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kerbal Space Program 2 announced|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/kerbal-space-program-2-announced/|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2019-08-19|last=Savage|first=Phil|work=PC Gamer|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218194443/https://www.pcgamer.com/kerbal-space-program-2-announced/|archive-date=2019-12-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Kerbal Space Program 2's new devs on adding interstellar flight, colonies and more to the PC's greatest space sim|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/kerbal-space-program-2-interview/|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2019-08-19|last=Savage|first=Phil|work=PC Gamer|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217204653/https://www.pcgamer.com/kerbal-space-program-2-interview/|archive-date=2019-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>Squad工作室将继续致力于优化、更新一代游戏。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Star Theory's shot beyond the Mun with Kerbal Space Program 2|url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-10-28-star-theorys-shot-beyond-the-mun-with-kerbal-space-program-2|accessdate=2020-03-03|work=GamesIndustry.biz|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210143727/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2019-10-28-star-theorys-shot-beyond-the-mun-with-kerbal-space-program-2|archive-date=2019-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>Private Division创建了一个新的工作室来开发续作，其中包括Star Theory工作室的成员。因此，Star Theory是否会出现在游戏界面上仍存变数。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Take-Two forms new studio for KSP2, with original developer’s role unclear|url=https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/take-two-forms-new-studio-for-ksp2-with-original-developers-role-unclear/|accessdate=2020-03-03|date=2020-02-20|work=VGC|language=en-GB|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200220172558/https://www.videogameschronicle.com/news/take-two-forms-new-studio-for-ksp2-with-original-developers-role-unclear/|archive-date=2020-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>
由于COVID-19大流行，这款游戏曾被推迟到2021年秋季发售。续作的创意总监Nate Simpson于2020年11月6日宣布了这款游戏发售日期跳票到2022年。<ref name="跳票2022">{{Cite web|title=《坎巴拉太空计划2》发售日期跳票到2022年|url=https://finance.sina.com.cn/tech/2020-11-06/doc-iiznctkc9904491.shtml|accessdate=2021-02-02|date=2020-11-06|last=cnBeta|work=finance.sina.com.cn}}</ref>

